    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Round</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">(Value) converts Value to the nearest integer.  In the case of a number that is exactly halfway between two integers, it converts it to whichever one is even.  See also </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Trunc" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Trunc</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></para>
